fields.title: Recipe - Spaghetti Bolognese
fields.body:
Ingredients:
- Spaghetti
- Ground beef
- Onion
- Garlic
- Tomato sauce
- Italian seasoning
- Parmesan cheese
Directions:
1. Cook spaghetti according to package instructions.
2. In a skillet, cook ground beef, onion, and garlic until browned.
3. Add tomato sauce and Italian seasoning, simmer for 15 minutes.
4. Serve over cooked spaghetti, garnish with Parmesan cheese.

fields.title: Book Summary - The Great Gatsby
fields.body:
Summary:
The Great Gatsby follows the lives of the narrator, Nick Carraway, and his mysterious neighbor Jay Gatsby. Set in the roaring twenties, the novel explores themes of love, wealth, and the American Dream. Gatsby's obsession with Daisy Buchanan leads to tragedy, highlighting the emptiness of materialism and the illusion of the American Dream.
